就瞬间变成醇厚的让牙齿不受控制咬合迷魂药了。这种在通感描述下应该陈述为粗砾的微微发糊的烟熏味（就如沙砾之于柔顺流水）是一种很自然很「亲切」、很容易被人类机体捕捉与领会到的、几乎等价于「这就是美味」的一种天然驱动力，它通过味蕾、神经元传输到你大脑后，你的所有递质都争先恐后去让你的牙齿快速咀嚼与吞咽，真是奇了怪了… 然后我还把自己舌头咬伤了… 最后，由于我先吃的熏制汉堡，后来再吃非熏制的汉堡时，一下就有比较，觉得那个普通煎制的肉排不够香。但我心里本身很排斥致癌的那些黑糊糊的玩意儿，平常也很久没吃熏制食品了。这就很奇怪。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7ed0e7e6ce621986af20f878592e7184_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/716578852"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIsJnw6MSklIFSEAMaCTExMDg5NjkyMCDf9/K3BjAAOJ8DQBJyCTcxNjU3ODg1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1728062361.103607", "card_id": "Q_292369449", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 183}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "真正的教育应该是什么样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b3b78e598881c757f5fc98065d495d1d_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/292369449"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsJnw6MSklIFSEAMaCDI3MjQ4MDU0INKYlNwFMAA46wdAE3IJMjkyMzY5NDQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1728062361.103796", "card_id": "Q_740112428", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "S14 瑞士轮次日 LNG 1:0 BLG 开赛二连胜距离晋级淘汰赛仅一步之遥，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "知乎电竞邀请各位答主参与长文创作活动，完成任务条件获取相应积分，电脑硬件及精美周边送不停>> 知乎追竞人"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-264d1f8234caa47cd3fc7b98b978ae64_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "12 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link":